  "title": "HSSEQ Executive (ISM/ISPS Codes, Marine)",
  "description": "<p><em>Our client is a leading provider of maritime energy solutions.</em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct and oversee quality checks of documentation following the company’s document control procedures in an ISO-certified environment, identifying and reporting any compliance issues.</li>\n  <li>Engage in incident investigations, ensuring that reports include root cause analysis and lessons learned are documented in the company’s database.</li>\n  <li>Oversee all HSEQ programs, generate status reports, and assist in the preparation of tender documents.</li>\n  <li>Support the ongoing enhancement of a positive safety culture.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Internal auditor for ISO 9001, 14001 and 45001 certified</li>\n  <li>Diploma in HSE/Marine Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of <strong>HSE </strong>experience in <strong>Marine/Shipping/Ship repair industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Knowledge of ISM and ISPS codes, incident investigation techniques and risk management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to<strong> hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
